This section introduces a motivating example to illustrate the test
generation for multiple languages and the effect of their unification.
Let us take as an example a prompt specification for the problem
of computing the derivative of a polynomial, as shown in Figure 1.
Figure 2 shows the results of test generation at temperature zero
for four target languages, namely for Java, Javascript (JS), C, and
